warning-coin-description-1-1: Fablo Coin is not subject to cash transactions and can be used for services within Fablo such as feature subscription or voting.
warning-coin-description-2-1: Until the termination of Fablo service.
warning-coin-description-3-1: The company may adjust some or all of the Fablo Coin for efficient use and operation of the service. Fablo Coin may be updated, discontinued, or expired as needed according to the company's policy and operational requirements.
warning-coin-description-3-2: If a member withdraws from the service or loses their eligibility to use the service, any Fablo coins acquired free of charge will automatically expire.
warning-coin-description-3-3: The company does not refund Fablo Coin that a customer spent. If it is confirmed that a member has accumulated or spent Fablo Coin through fraudulent means, the company may reclaim the fraudulently obtained Fablo Coin and take actions such as suspending activities, imposing restrictions, or filing criminal charges.
warning-coin-description-4-1: If there is an error in accumulating Fablo Coin, the member can request a correction from the company within 30 days of the occurrence of the error or the day the member became aware of the error. If the request is confirmed to be legitimate, the company will take corrective action within 30 days from the date of the request.
